tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE tee_time_reservations (
  reservation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  player_name VARCHAR(50),
  tee_time DATETIME,
  golf_course_name VARCHAR(100),
  booking_method VARCHAR(20)
);

CREATE TABLE TeeTimeReservations (
    reservation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    player_name VARCHAR(50),
    tee_time DATETIME,
    course_id INT,
    CONSTRAINT fk_course FOREIGN KEY (course_id) REFERENCES GolfCourses(course_id)
);

CREATE TABLE TeeTimes (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 tee_time TIMESTAMP,
 player_id INT,
 golf_course_id INT,
 FOREIGN KEY (player_id) REFERENCES Players(id),
 FOREIGN KEY (golf_course_id) REFERENCES GolfCourses(id)
);

CREATE TABLE Reservations (
 id INT PRIMARY KEY,
 tee_time_id INT,
 player_id INT,
 status VARCHAR(20),
 FOREIGN KEY (tee_time_id) REFERENCES TeeTimes(id),
 FOREIGN KEY (player_id) REFERENCES Players(id)
);

CREATE TABLE tee_times (
  tee_time_id INT,
  course_id INT,
  player_id INT,
  tee_time_date DATE,
  PRIMARY KEY (tee_time_id)
);

CREATE TABLE courses (
  course_id INT,
  course_name VARCHAR(50),
  course_location VARCHAR(100),
  course_rating DECIMAL(3, 1),
  PRIMARY KEY (course_id)
);

CREATE TABLE players (
  player_id INT,
  player_name VARCHAR(50),
  player_email VARCHAR(100),
  player_phone VARCHAR(15),
  player_handicap DECIMAL(3, 1),
  PRIMARY KEY (player_id)
);

CREATE TABLE reservations (
  reservation_id INT,
  tee_time_id INT,
  player_id INT,
  reservation_time TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (reservation_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (tee_time_id) REFERENCES tee_times(tee_time_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (player_id) REFERENCES players(player_id)
);

CREATE TABLE tee_time_history (
  history_id INT,
  tee_time_id INT,
  reservation_id INT,
  played_date DATE,
  score INT,
  PRIMARY KEY (history_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (tee_time_id) REFERENCES tee_times(tee_time_id),
  FOREIGN KEY (reservation_id) REFERENCES reservations(reservation_id)
);
